    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, you called it a \"misconception\"? That seems a bit one-sided. People argue that government-run systems lead to long wait times, lower quality of care, and huge tax burdens. Are those points just wrong, or are they actually valid concerns about how these systems work?",
